item.title: Alonzo Williams: Eazy E Dying of AIDS Was A Set Up!
item.description:
After weeks of jab's from our own MC EIht, World Class Wrecking Crew's Alonzo Williams pulls up to set the record straight. We talk about him, Dr Dre and DJ Yella's early days, how he plugged Eazy E up with the infamous Jerry Heller. He then talk's about how inaccurate his character portrayal's in the NWA movie and R&B sensation Michel'le's biopic were.
